    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In roofing, strips of wood fixed to the upper side of rafters at the eaves, that raise the edge of the eaves and form a break in the roof line.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
